name: Somette_Liberty_Light_Oak_2-piece_Dining_Set
reviews: Putting the table together was a breeze, the quality is very strong, and heavy. There is also an extender that comes with the table. It brings a glamorous look to any eat in kitchen with a touch of coziness.
Awesome set, so glad I purchased it.
description: This table features light oak 3D paper with a brushed stainless steel dining base. The table includes a self storing extension that easily extends from 51.18 inches to 66.93 inches. The fully upholstered nook adds to the flair of the table. This bench is sturdy and comfortable, giving ample seating space for your family or guests. Set includes: One (1) table, one (1) nookMaterials: Stainless steel, woodFinish/color: Light oak, neutral beige and grey weaveTable dimensions: 29.53 inches high x 51.18 inches wide x 31.5 inches deepNook dimensions: 33.46 inches high x 50.39 inches wide x  70.08 inches longStyleCasual, Contemporary, TraditionalMaterialSteel, Upholstered, WoodFinishOak Finish, Wood FinishShapeRectangleAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBeige, Grey, Off-White, Tan, TaupeFurniture PatternSolid
